### Welcome to MC CTI Generator
This Custom Textured Item (CTI) Generator is the simplest, fastest, and most beautiful way to generate items and JSON files allowing for your own custom textured items in Minecraft.

### Authors and Contributors
This addition was inspired by David Mulvey and created in cooperation with [creatiOS](cosisme.ga), [</SYP>](Sypisme.ga) and Julian Sanchez.

###JSON Output
Let's say I wanted to add three items with a base of carrot on a stick this is want the generator would output:
models/items/carrot_on_a_stick:

```
{
 "parent": "item/handheld_rod",
    "textures": {items/carrot_on_a_stick"
        "layer0": "items/carrot_on_a_stick"
    },
    "overrides": [
        {"predicate": {"damage": 0.25},"model": "item/carrot_on_a_stick_1"},
        {"predicate": {"damage": 0.5},"model": "item/carrot_on_a_stick_2"},
        {"predicate": {"damage": 0.75},"model": "item/carrot_on_a_stick_3"}
    ]
}
```
 and would create three files in the following format:

models/item/carrot_on_a_stick_1:
```
{
    "parent": "item/generated",
    "textures": {
        "layer0": "items/[texture goes here]"
    }
}
